## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to design a runtime-extendable plugin system with isolation, dependency injection, and concurrency considerations. It also probes trade-offs between Plugin and Strategy patterns.

## Key Concepts

- Plugin pattern
- Registry for runtime extensibility
- Dependency Injection via a shared container
