## Why This Is Asked

Assess ability to design runtime-extensible components, manage threading, and reason about cache behavior in large-scale systems.

## Key Concepts

- Runtime registries for strategy extension
- Thread-safe, lock-free reads with bounded memory
- Eviction and read-through refresh choreography

## Code Example

```typescript
interface EvictionPolicy<K, V> {
  onPut(key: K, value: V, currentSize: number): number;
